{"tid":1624423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚原來係一個伏！係一個伏呀！","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:25:22.000Z","uid":233745,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe6fb83b76565ac6c8470ee8397d94e12de6748","tid":1624423,"uid":233745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"(如果認同既幫幫手推唔該)<br />\n<br />\n琴晚點解popo無大拘捕？？？<br />\n唯一既解釋就係政府想逆轉民意！等中立同和理非既市民覺得得我地既行為好暴力，會同我地割蓆！到時成場運動就會失敗告中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道大家好嬲，我同大家一樣都係。但希望大家唔好破壞藍底既鋪頭，如果唔係呢場運動民意逆轉我地就會輸！！所以我地要保持理性！我知道大家都唔想輸！！<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"a7a3f962b1bb06374ad7e50d1a44106debf101c1","tid":1624423,"uid":197149,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"好暴力咩？唔覺喎"},{"pid":"e10a7d1d5a95861f499b1c6de2c21a64ff1eb342","tid":1624423,"uid":233745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a7a3f962b1bb06374ad7e50d1a44106debf101c1","tid":1624423,"uid":197149,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"好暴力咩？唔覺喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"我怕和理非既市民會覺"},{"pid":"17468f62b06f57761406227f5854ed98a46e91f5","tid":1624423,"uid":167939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"咩暴力啊 尋晚打風有幾個車站 幾間鋪頭冇做好防風嘅準備 爆咗玻璃 關示威咩事？"},{"pid":"feb45d087946a9fa877138920abac923205d18cb","tid":1624423,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"民意從來唔會少  只會不斷增加"},{"pid":"b7ff82367fa995f305ed580542a768a1522e7a42","tid":1624423,"uid":233745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17468f62b06f57761406227f5854ed98a46e91f5","tid":1624423,"uid":167939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:53:06